  "time_ut": 1660545177,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dba\u0dbd \u0d9a\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dba\u0dda \u0dc0\u0dd3 \u0db8\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0daf\u0dd3 \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0db1\u0dd3\u0db8 \u0db8\u0dda \u0dc3\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dda \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0da7\u0db8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Buying paddy in the spring season from this week",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Minister of Agriculture Mahinda Amaraweera said that steps will be taken to start the purchase of paddy crops in the green season from this week and today (15th) a Cabinet paper will be submitted for the approval of the Cabinet.",
        "The second food outlet of the National Food Promotion Board was opened by the minister at Hunupitiya Commercial Fertilizer Corporation premises today (15th) morning. This outlet was established under the program of establishing food outlets by the National Food Promotion Board to provide the public with the opportunity to buy food items at an affordable price.",
        "Compared to that, the commercial fertilizer company's fertilizer store was also opened.",
        "Addressing the people who participated in this event, the minister announced that the paddy marketing board will start buying the paddy harvest of the new season from this week by giving a good price to the farmers.",
        "The fertilizer distribution program in the Yala season was very successful. Some people accused us of releasing inferior and toxic fertilizers to the farmers. But all those accusations are false today. The farmers themselves say that the urea fertilizers we provided are of the highest quality. Our goal is organic. The Minister of Agriculture said that the Department of Agriculture has recommended cultivation using both types of chemical fertilizers under the percentage of 70:30 from next month.",
        "Through this system of outlets established by the National Food Promotion Board, the consumers will be given the opportunity to buy food items at a concessional price. Also, the producers of food items will also be given the opportunity to sell their products. Our aim is to make the Ministry of Agriculture a ministry that goes beyond the targeted programs The Minister also mentioned that the support of all those working under the Ministry of Agriculture should be received in order to achieve that goal.",
        "The chairman of the National Food Promotion Board, Mr. Palinda Sagara, Commissioner of the Department of Agricultural Development, Mr. AHML Abeyratne, and the presidents of Lanka Fertilizer Company and Commercial Fertilizer Company participated in this event."
      ],
